@new_congreso_elections
title: Force new elections!
subtitle: We are the kingmakers with this arithmetics after all
choose-if: congreso_coalition_force_elections
unavailable-subtitle: This is out of our control
on-arrival: {!
    Q.next_spanish_election_month += 4;
    if (Q.next_spanish_election_month >= 12) {
        Q.next_spanish_election_month = Q.next_spanish_election_month % 12;
        Q.next_spanish_election_year = Q.year + 1;
    } else {
        Q.next_spanish_election_year = Q.year;
    }
    if (Q.rubicon) {
        Q.next_spanish_election_time += 4 * 4;
    } else {
        Q.next_spanish_election_time += 4;
        Q[Q.player_party + "_congreso_catalunya_support"] -= 2.5;
    }

    if (Q.congreso_coalition_left_reach) {
        if (Q.csqp_formed) {
            Q.csqp_relations -= 10;
        } else if (Q.cecp_formed) {
            Q.cecp_relations -= 10;
        } else if (Q.ecp_formed) {
            Q.ecp_relations -= 10;
        } else {
            Q.icv_relations -= 10;
        }
    } else if (Q.congreso_coalition_change_reach) {
        if (Q.csqp_formed) {
            Q.csqp_relations -= 7;
        } else if (Q.cecp_formed) {
            Q.cecp_relations -= 7;
        } else if (Q.ecp_formed) {
            Q.ecp_relations -= 7;
        } else {
            Q.icv_relations -= 7;
        }
        Q.psc_relations -= 5;
    } else if (Q.congreso_coalition_progressive_reach) {
        if (Q.csqp_formed) {
            Q.csqp_relations -= 5;
        } else if (Q.cecp_formed) {
            Q.cecp_relations -= 5;
        } else if (Q.ecp_formed) {
            Q.ecp_relations -= 5;
        } else {
            Q.icv_relations -= 5;
        }
        Q.psc_relations -= 7;
    }
!}

While definitely an unpopular option with some, we've decided that these results were not for us. 

- @post_event: We have to hope this is for the better...


